《'''THE ALBUM'''》是[[韓國|韓國]]女子音樂組合[[BLACKPINK|BLACKPINK]]的首張韓語正規專輯<ref>{{cite news |title=ENHYPEN, BTS, NCT and more reign over the top spots on Billboard’s World Albums Chart |url=https://www.pinkvilla.com/entertainment/enhypen-bts-nct-and-more-reign-over-top-spots-billboard-s-world-albums-chart-1012544 |accessdate=2022-02-07 |work=PINKVILLA |date=2022-02-02 |language=en |archive-date=2022-02-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220207122200/https://www.pinkvilla.com/entertainment/enhypen-bts-nct-and-more-reign-over-top-spots-billboard-s-world-albums-chart-1012544 }}</ref>，該專輯於2020年8月28日開始預售<ref name="#3">{{cite web |url=https://koreajoongangdaily.joins.com/2020/08/28/entertainment/kpop/Blackpink-The-Album-fulllength-album/20200828163907058.html |title=Preorders begin for Blackpink's first full-length album |date=2020-08-28 |4= |publisher=koreajoongangdaily |language=en |accessdate=2020-09-29 |archive-date=2020-09-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200910021944/https://koreajoongangdaily.joins.com/2020/08/28/entertainment/kpop/Blackpink-The-Album-fulllength-album/20200828163907058.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，並於10月2日正式發行<ref>{{cite web |url=https://pitchfork.com/news/blackpink-announce-new-album/ |title=BLACKPINK Announce New Album |date=2020-07-28 |4= |publisher=Pitchfork |language=en |accessdate=2020-09-29 |archive-date=2020-08-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200822190204/https://pitchfork.com/news/blackpink-announce-new-album/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。專輯中包含先前釋出的先行曲《[[How_You_Like_That|How You Like That]]》與數位單曲《[[Ice_Cream_(歌曲)|Ice Cream]]》在內共收錄了八首歌曲，主打曲為《[[Lovesick_Girls|Lovesick Girls]]》。此專輯讓BLACKPINK成為KPOP歷史上第一個GAON榜單銷量破百萬女歌手，《THE ALBUM》以1,073,671的銷量站上了10月GAON專輯銷售榜單的第二名，也是女歌手中第一個GAON榜單銷量突破100萬張的專輯。<ref>{{cite news |title=ENHYPEN, BTS, NCT, TXT, TWICE, BLACKPINK, And ITZY Claim Top Spots On Billboard’s World Albums Chart |url=https://www.soompi.com/article/1511016wpp/enhypen-bts-nct-txt-twice-blackpink-and-itzy-claim-top-spots-on-billboards-world-albums-chart |accessdate=2022-02-07 |work=Soompi |date=1643731784 |language=en |archive-date=2022-03-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220319045654/https://www.soompi.com/article/1511016wpp/enhypen-bts-nct-txt-twice-blackpink-and-itzy-claim-top-spots-on-billboards-world-albums-chart }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last1=Manongdo |first1=Jennifer |title=Blackpink’s ‘Ddu-Du-Ddu-Du’ Becomes Second K-Pop Video To Reach 1.8B Views On YouTube |url=https://www.ibtimes.com/blackpinks-ddu-du-ddu-du-becomes-second-k-pop-video-reach-18b-views-youtube-3388497 |accessdate=2022-02-07 |work=International Business Times |date=2022-02-02 |archive-date=2022-02-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220207122220/https://www.ibtimes.com/blackpinks-ddu-du-ddu-du-becomes-second-k-pop-video-reach-18b-views-youtube-3388497 }}</ref>

== 背景與發行 ==
起初YG娛樂於2020年6月1日稱BLACKPINK將於9月攜帶首張正規專輯回歸<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.thestar.com.my/lifestyle/entertainment/2020/06/01/solo-tracks-planned-for-blackpink-members-rose-lisa-and-jisoo |title=Solo tracks planned for Blackpink members, Rose, Lisa and Jisoo |language=en |publisher=TheStar |date=2020-06-01 |accessdate=2020-06-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200608003302/https://www.thestar.com.my/lifestyle/entertainment/2020/06/01/solo-tracks-planned-for-blackpink-members-rose-lisa-and-jisoo |archive-date=2020-06-08 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，隨後7月28日官方宣布專輯正式定於10月2日發布<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.billboard.com/amp/articles/columns/k-town/9425409/blackpink-debut-album-release-date |title=Blackpink to Release Debut Album This Fall |language=en |publisher=Billboard |date=2020-07-28 |accessdate=2020-07-28 |archive-date=2020-07-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200728025211/https://www.billboard.com/amp/articles/columns/k-town/9425409/blackpink-debut-album-release-date |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2020年6月26日，專輯先行曲《[[How_You_Like_That|How You Like That]]》發布；8月28日，收錄於專輯中的數位單曲《[[Ice_Cream_(歌曲)|Ice Cream]]》發布。

9月21日，官方公布概念海報<ref>{{cite tweet |user=BLACKPINKOFFICIAL |number=1307847013137080320|date=2020-09-21 |title=#BLACKPINK #블랙핑크 #1stFULLALBUM #THEALBUM #20201002_12amEST #20201002_1pmKST #COMINGSOON #YG}}</ref>。9月22日，公布Jisoo預告海報<ref>{{cite tweet |user=BLACKPINKOFFICIAL |number=1308194298895114243|date=2020-09-22 |title='THE ALBUM’ JISOO TEASER POSTER #1}}</ref><ref>{{cite tweet |user=BLACKPINKOFFICIAL |number=1308299993716084736|date=2020-09-22 |title='THE ALBUM’ JISOO TEASER POSTER #2}}</ref>。9月23日，公布Jennie預告海報<ref>{{cite tweet |user=BLACKPINKOFFICIAL |number=1308556685112479744|date=2020-09-23 |title='THE ALBUM’ JENNIE TEASER POSTER #1}}</ref><ref>{{cite tweet |user=BLACKPINKOFFICIAL |number=1308662385960464384|date=2020-09-23 |title='THE ALBUM’ JENNIE TEASER POSTER #2}}</ref>。9月24日，公布Lisa預告海報<ref>{{cite tweet |user=BLACKPINKOFFICIAL |number=1308919074890477570|date=2020-09-24 |title='THE ALBUM’ LISA TEASER POSTER #1}}</ref><ref>{{cite tweet |user=BLACKPINKOFFICIAL |number=1309024770319618070|date=2020-09-24 |title='THE ALBUM’ LISA TEASER POSTER #2}}</ref>。9月25日，公布Rosé預告海報<ref>{{cite tweet |user=BLACKPINKOFFICIAL |number=1309281465402884096?s=19|date=2020-09-25 |title=‘THE ALBUM’ ROSÉ TEASER POSTER #1}}</ref><ref>{{cite tweet |user=BLACKPINKOFFICIAL |number=1309387160324247553|date=2020-09-25 |title=‘THE ALBUM’ ROSÉ TEASER POSTER #2}}</ref>。9月27日，公布各成員的概念預告影片<ref>{{cite tweet |user=BLACKPINKOFFICIAL |number=1310006240177721346|date=2020-09-27 |title='THE ALBUM' LISA Concept Teaser Video}}</ref><ref>{{cite tweet |user=BLACKPINKOFFICIAL |number=1310006488623132672|date=2020-09-27 |title='THE ALBUM' ROSÉ Concept Teaser Video}}</ref><ref>{{cite tweet |user=BLACKPINKOFFICIAL |number=1310111934629294080|date=2020-09-28 |title='THE ALBUM' JISOO Concept Teaser Video}}</ref><ref>{{cite tweet |user=BLACKPINKOFFICIAL |number=1310112184916115456|date=2020-09-28 |title='THE ALBUM' JENNIE Concept Teaser Video}}</ref>。9月28日，公布主打曲《[[Lovesick_Girls|Lovesick Girls]]》預告海報及預告影片<ref>{{cite tweet |user=BLACKPINKOFFICIAL |number=1310368625262436353|date=2020-09-28 |title=‘Lovesick Girls’ TEASER POSTER}}</ref><ref>{{cite tweet |user=BLACKPINKOFFICIAL |number=1310474324373979136|date=2020-09-28 |title='Lovesick Girls' Concept Teaser Video}}</ref>。9月30日，公布《Lovesick Girls》MV預告<ref>{{cite tweet |user=BLACKPINKOFFICIAL |number=1311093405519237120|date=2020-09-30 |title='Lovesick Girls' M/V TEASER}}</ref>。

